The natural skincare range from Pigeon has been specially formulated with extracts of Jojoba and Chamomile to provide the best results to the baby’s skin. The Baby Wash from Pigeon is also good for the baby’s scalp as Jojoba has the properties to cleanse the skin and scalp of dirt and grime. You can pour adequate amount of the Baby Wash 2 in 1 into a sponge and lather it up on your bundle of joy’s body and hair. Rinse it off completely to let your baby feel refreshed.
